snippet.title: Farming Simulator C64 Edition
snippet.description:
Farm Like Before! The Farming SImulator C64 Edition is a bonus content of the Farming Simulator 19 Collectors Edition. The game comes with the appropriate emulator so you can play it on your PC.

► Website: http://www.farming-simulator.com/ 
► Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/giants.farming.simulator 
► Twitter: https://twitter.com/farmingsim
► Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/giantsfarmingsimulator/

The multiplatform hit series expands to one of the most popular gaming systems ever.

Available Late 2018
 
More Information on the official website: http://www.farming-simulator.com/newsArticle.php?&news_id=88
